{"tid":2342452,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"遼寧開原狂漢街頭擸刀斬人 最少7死7傷","createTime":"2020-12-27T06:45:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-27T12:28:06.000Z","uid":28202,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"10877bc527c1af29cbc3c463c79017bef1be1e02","tid":2342452,"uid":28202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T06:45:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201227/6IPTE646XFAXJOFLG3C4BVMXMM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201227%2F6IPTE646XFAXJOFLG3C4BVMXMM%2F&d=sZqGLlkYYIxatccyfr7NWEcGFqE5jXx4AE4DM0839cs%3D&h=52d7fa3e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201227%2F6IPTE646XFAXJOFLG3C4BVMXMM%2F&h=dfc44c9b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201227/6IPTE646XFAXJOFLG3C4BVMXMM/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/U5h2gDfDNYK1o3fBWvQ9m_ol8C0=/720x405/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/DO6ATQ3PUZDGTEZALDTWJJMFQ4.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FU5h2gDfDNYK1o3fBWvQ9m_ol8C0%3D%2F720x405%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FDO6ATQ3PUZDGTEZALDTWJJMFQ4.jpeg&h=d1093316&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n遼寧省鐵嶺開原市今早發生斬人案，一名男子今早在當地一間洗浴中心門外，見人就斬，造成最少7死7傷，傷者中包括一名警員，疑犯已被當局拘捕，未知行兇動機。<br />\n<br />\n內地官媒指，事發在今早8時14分，一名男子在開原市老友誼飯店二部附近、一間名叫金普盛浴的洗浴中心外行兇。多名傷者被斬後，倒臥地上，等候救援，街道上有警員駐守。內媒取得的閉路電視片段則顯示，男子行兇後逃走，在路上被兩名警員截住，其中一名警員抓起一個掃把，攻擊行兇者，三人扭打一輪後男子被按倒地上，其他民眾亦上前協助。<br />\n<br />\n當地宣傳部稱，行兇男子名叫楊Ｘ峰，已經被警員拘捕，未知他的行兇動機，僅表示案件正在進一步偵辦中。"},{"pid":"117e850cd5c6b30791af98545650d04a5afc538b","tid":2342452,"uid":77717,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T06:46:51.000Z","msg":"來生不做支那人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6e961b546003220ad9182ac73fc63ab9aed5603","tid":2342452,"ui